00:29:43,744 --> 00:29:48,204
Please let her go. I beg of you.

253
00:29:51,552 --> 00:29:59,459
Il-mae! I never even got a chance
to show you how much I love you.

254
00:30:00,561 --> 00:30:03,826
Just give me one chance!

255
00:30:11,772 --> 00:30:13,330
He looks just like a weasel

256
00:30:16,110 --> 00:30:19,170
Tonight is not the first night
we're sleeping together.

257
00:30:20,114 --> 00:30:24,016
We've done it countless times.

258
00:30:25,519 --> 00:30:27,248
So, don't bother me anymore.

259
00:30:28,889 --> 00:30:32,120
You bitch! Bother you?

260
00:30:32,693 --> 00:30:36,823
I've been bothering you?
How about me?

261
00:30:37,564 --> 00:30:41,694
You think I enjoyed packing
your lunch for 4 years?

262
00:30:42,436 --> 00:30:44,802
And reserving your seat at the library?

263
00:30:45,606 --> 00:30:52,011
Do you think doing your
laundry was fun?

264
00:30:54,315 --> 00:30:56,078
Really?

265
00:31:07,461 --> 00:31:11,898
It's nice to know
how you really felt.

266
00:31:13,400 --> 00:31:15,095
Can I go now?

267
00:31:17,805 --> 00:31:25,541
Get out of my sight!
You make me want to puke!

268
00:31:26,313 --> 00:31:29,077
No, I'll go.

269
00:31:29,149 --> 00:31:36,612
I'm so shamed I wasted my life
chasing after a slut like you!

270
00:32:37,951 --> 00:32:42,411
What? I ask you to go to Seoul

271
00:32:42,489 --> 00:32:44,957
