investigate Il-mae's affairs.

272
00:32:45,025 --> 00:32:48,620
And, now you
return and cry like a girl.

273
00:32:51,298 --> 00:32:54,893
Il-mae went to the hospital.

274
00:32:54,968 --> 00:32:57,266
So, I thought she's gonna see
a gynecologist.

275
00:32:59,740 --> 00:33:01,571
Hospital?

276
00:33:17,658 --> 00:33:20,456
She has the myelodysplastic
syndromes,

277
00:33:21,161 --> 00:33:26,030
the same illness that
took away your wife.

278
00:33:26,099 --> 00:33:27,794
Oh, lord.

279
00:34:02,769 --> 00:34:12,508
Teacher, you're so light.
You got no meat on your legs.

280
00:34:13,914 --> 00:34:15,779
You've gotten so thin.

281
00:34:17,317 --> 00:34:22,983
You need to eat more.

282
00:34:25,158 --> 00:34:31,188
I'm not light.
You've become stronger.

283
00:34:31,431 --> 00:34:33,365
Tae-il.

284
00:34:34,535 --> 00:34:36,230
Yes, teacher.

285
00:34:38,405 --> 00:34:40,873
Are you really ok?

286
00:34:41,742 --> 00:34:46,645
Of course. I'm fine.

287
00:34:48,015 --> 00:34:52,179
It's not a big deal to me

288
00:34:54,421 --> 00:34:59,586
The funny thing is, the date for the
2nd exam is the same date

289
00:35:01,028 --> 00:35:05,465
as Il-mae's wedding date.

290
00:35:06,300 --> 00:35:12,603
Good. There is no reason why
you should attend her wedding.

291
00:35:15,542 --> 00:35:22,277
Go on and do well on your exam
and pass it with flying colors.

292
00:35:23,817 --> 00:35:25,546
Don't worry about me.

293
00:35:28,021 --> 00:35:36,827
I'll pass the exam... get married...
have kids...

294
00:35:38,665 --> 00:35:42,658
then I will come back to see you.

295
00:35:44,404 --> 00:35:56,805
I'll never forget...
all you've done for me.

296
00:35:58,151 --> 00:36:00,847
Alright.

297
00:36:37,224 --> 00:36:39,954
Who is it? Dad?

298
00:36:48,435 --> 00:36:50,335
Dad, Dad!

299
00:36:50,404 --> 00:36:53,498
Tae-il... Tae-il...

300
00:37:10,257 --> 00:37:14,591
Tae-il! SOHN Tae-il!

301
00:37:26,606 --> 00:37:28,471
JOO Il-mae!

302
00:37:29,943 --> 00:37:31,001
Yes?

303
00:37:31,578 --> 00:37:33,341
Eat well and live well!

304
00:37:35,082 --> 00:37:36,344
Eat well and...

305
00:37:39,753 --> 00:37:41,550
don't get sick, ok?

306
00:37:44,691 --> 00:37:52,223
If you do get sick,
don't get too sick. Ok?

307
00:37:55,135 --> 00:38:03,338
You too! Don't get into
any more troubles!

308
00:38:03,410 --> 00:38:08,643
And don't be so stubborn, ok?

309
00:38:10,117 --> 00:38:17,250
Stop worrying about me.

310
00:38:17,324 --> 00:38:20,487
I'll be fine.

311
00:38:25,065 --> 00:38:27,898
Goodbye.

312
00:38:45,385 --> 00:38:52,314
Tae-il! Do you know why
I'm marrying him?

313
00:38:53,460 --> 00:38:57,920
Because he has other women.

314
00:38:59,199 --> 00:39:05,195
He'll easily fall in love again.

315
00:39:09,643 --> 00:39:12,009
Even without me,

316
00:39:12,078 --> 00:39:16,811
he'll continue to live
a happy life!

317
00:39:18,151 --> 00:39:25,648
But, you can't do that.

318
00:39:26,459 --> 00:39:29,292
You'll only think of me
and love me!

319
00:39:29,362 --> 00:39:38,202
Just like my dad!

320
00:39:39,706 --> 00:39:46,077
I can't let you become
like my dad.

321
00:39:49,449 --> 00:39:58,949
Dad, I'm not a bad person,
am I?

322
00:40:01,328 --> 00:40:04,695
Of course not.

323
00:40:08,535 --> 00:40:18,410
Like a flower... like a star...
you're the loveliest girl in the world...

324
00:40:28,054 --> 00:40:33,651
Dad, let's practice the wedding march.

325
00:40:35,629 --> 00:40:43,263
We have to be careful
not to step on my dress.

326
00:40:46,306 --> 00:40:50,174
Alright, alright.

327
00:42:04,684 --> 00:42:12,113
Il-mae!!!

328
00:43:17,424 --> 00:43:21,360
- Tilt your head a bit to the left.
- Turn it just a little.

329
00:43:30,437 --> 00:43:33,634
My love, do you know
what I did today?

330
00:43:36,709 --> 00:43:42,670
I went to the photo studio with
Il-mae and took pictures.

331
00:43:44,551 --> 00:43:50,114
She braided her hair and
wore this really pretty dress.

332
00:43:52,092 --> 00:43:57,758
And we took a picture together.

333
00:44:01,434 --> 00:44:06,303
She was trying to do what
you and I couldn't do.

334
00:44:10,009 --> 00:44:18,883
Do you know what she said to me
as she took her portrait?

335
00:44:21,387 --> 00:44:33,766
She smiled and said,

336
00:44:36,402 --> 00:44:43,672
"Dad, I've a very happy life.

337
00:44:44,277 --> 00:44:51,513
So please don't cry
when you look at this picture."

338
00:44:52,986 --> 00:44:59,653
And she smiled.

339
00:45:03,730 --> 00:45:09,691
My lovely child... my sweet child...

340
00:45:17,010 --> 00:45:22,312
Teacher, you're killing yourself.
Please don't do this.

341
00:45:33,660 --> 00:45:36,128
The 45th Level 2
bar exam center

342
00:45:44,137 --> 00:45:45,934
Begin.

343
00:46:16,069 --> 00:46:23,942
It would be much appreciated
if you'd participated in blood drive.

344
00:46:25,245 --> 00:46:26,803
What the hell are you saying?

345
00:46:26,879 --> 00:46:31,680
Of course it's our duty as his students
to do as much as we can.

346
00:46:38,958 --> 00:46:41,358
- What's going on?
- Get off me!! You bastards!

347
00:46:41,427 --> 00:46:43,827
SOHN Tae-il! You bastard!

348
00:46:43,896 --> 00:46:46,421
How can you take a test right now?

349
00:46:46,499 --> 00:46:49,798
Tae-il, come out here! You know
what Il-mae did for you?

350
00:46:50,870 --> 00:46:53,896
Get off me! She... Tae-il, she's...

351
00:46:53,973 --> 00:46:59,138
Tae-il doesn't understand why.

352
00:46:59,679 --> 00:47:03,115
He's just trying to forget her
because she told him to.

353
00:47:03,916 --> 00:47:10,344
Come on! Step on the accelerator!

354
00:47:11,424 --> 00:47:18,728
He has no clue that she's doing
this for his own sake

355
00:47:20,033 --> 00:47:22,866
For the only person she ever loved...

356
00:47:24,203 --> 00:47:28,435
she wants him to be happy
even when she's not here anymore.

357
00:47:30,076 --> 00:47:34,570
My love, what am I supposed to do?

358
00:47:35,181 --> 00:47:39,413
What can I do?

359
00:47:40,386 --> 00:47:47,053
I now pronounce you to be
husband and wife.

360
00:47:51,898 --> 00:47:54,059
Nonsense!

361
00:48:00,373 --> 00:48:05,037
- Nullify this marriage!
- Nullify! Nullify!

362
00:48:05,111 --> 00:48:07,944
What the hell do you think
you're doing?

363
00:48:08,014 --> 00:48:15,386
Ladies and gentlemen, this girl
right here, is a horrible person!

364
00:48:16,856 --> 00:48:18,551
This stupid girl...

365
00:48:19,559 --> 00:48:24,360
She's suffering from the same illness
which took her mom away...

366
00:48:25,798 --> 00:48:30,167
So I can live happily by myself...

367
00:48:31,204 --> 00:48:38,542
So I can pass the exam and
live happily by myself!

368
00:48:38,845 --> 00:48:44,511
Il-mae, did you really think
I'd be fine?

369
00:48:46,519 --> 00:48:50,455
I already gave you my heart.

370
00:48:51,391 --> 00:48:56,522
How am I supposed to
live without you?

371
00:49:01,534 --> 00:49:05,595
And our teacher...
he's a horrible person, too.

372
00:49:10,743 --> 00:49:12,802
As her father...

373
00:49:12,879 --> 00:49:23,050
this is how he shows his love.

374
00:49:34,000 --> 00:49:42,135
Tae-il, why are you doing this to her?

375
00:49:43,743 --> 00:49:48,203
What can she do now?

376
00:49:48,281 --> 00:49:51,842
That's exactly why
I cannot allow this marriage.

377
00:49:52,685 --> 00:49:58,487
If you'd known your wife's gonna die,
would you've not loved her?

378
00:49:59,258 --> 00:50:02,022
Answer me!

379
00:50:19,011 --> 00:50:20,239
Il-mae!

380
00:50:24,650 --> 00:50:29,383
I never regret loving your mother.

381
00:50:31,390 --> 00:50:36,987
Your mother was the best thing
that ever happened to me.

382
00:50:39,131 --> 00:50:53,205
Even now, everyday of my life is
filled of joy because your mom!

383
00:51:07,159 --> 00:51:12,461
Please, forgive her.

384
00:51:13,766 --> 00:51:15,358
And please release her.

385
00:51:17,270 --> 00:51:23,800
Allow me to be at her side
till her last day.

386
00:51:24,710 --> 00:51:29,044
- Please release her.
- Please! Release her!

387
00:51:38,558 --> 00:51:44,497
This marriage is... nullified!

388
00:52:11,290 --> 00:52:23,361
Tae-il! I'm sick.
And I'll get sicker.

389
00:52:25,504 --> 00:52:36,210
I'm afraid I won't be able to
be with you much longer

390
00:52:38,618 --> 00:52:44,853
You can't die. I won't let you.

391
00:52:48,794 --> 00:52:52,787
Forget the law school! I'll study
and go to a medical school

392
00:52:52,865 --> 00:52:57,063
I'm gonna find out a cure
for your illness

393
00:53:18,324 --> 00:53:20,417
I pretended I was asleep

394
00:53:20,493 --> 00:53:24,452
and he's already snoring. Little fool...

395
00:53:26,866 --> 00:53:32,532
Our first kiss was a long awaited one...

396
00:53:34,173 --> 00:53:41,136
Thinking about our first kiss
still makes my heart flutter...

397
00:53:50,056 --> 00:53:52,081
I love you, Tae-il!

398
00:53:55,361 --> 00:54:05,965
Teacher, I can't say that!

399
00:54:10,443 --> 00:54:11,876
Tae-il.

400
00:54:22,388 --> 00:54:31,023
I can't... I can't do that here.

401
00:54:51,317 --> 00:54:56,880
Let go of her, will you?
Let go of her.

402
00:54:59,959 --> 00:55:04,896
Never! I'll never let her go!

403
00:55:05,965 --> 00:55:14,134
I'm gonna cure her illness and
we're gonna live happily together

404
00:55:15,007 --> 00:55:19,842
till our deaths do us apart
teeth fall out.
